OL,3,CAsda set to axe 1,000 jobs as
OL,4,Csupermarket expands use of robots in
OL,5,Cwarehouses
OL,7,FUp to 1,000 jobs are set to be lost as
OL,8,FAsda accelerates the use of automation
OL,9,Facross its warehouse operations.
OL,11,FThe supermarket is relocating its
OL,12,FGeorge clothing online operations from
OL,13,Fthree sites in Northampton,
OL,14,FStaffordshire and Tyne and Wear to a
OL,15,Fsingle site in Derby, operated by DHL.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780611061
OL,3,CAsda set to axe 1,000 jobs as
OL,4,Csupermarket expands use of robots in
OL,5,Cwarehouses
OL,7,F1,250 Asda employees are scheduled to
OL,8,Ftransfer to DHL as part of the
OL,9,Fchanges, but at a consultation meeting
OL,10,Fwith the GMB Union two weeks ago, DHL
OL,11,Frevealed that only 250 workers would
OL,12,Fbe required at the new warehouse.
OL,14,FThe site in Derby is being fitted with
OL,15,F"Redline" robots - an automated system
OL,16,Fdeveloped by the Norwegian company
OL,17,FAutoStore.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
