OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780611061
OL,3,CAsda set to axe 1,000 jobs as
OL,4,Csupermarket expands use of robots in
OL,5,Cwarehouses
OL,7,FIn its promotional material, AutoStore
OL,8,Fsays the robotic technology allows
OL,9,Fretailers to store more stock in less
OL,10,Fspace and process orders faster by
OL,11,Fautomating the retrieval of products
OL,12,Fthat would previously have been picked
OL,13,Fmanually by warehouse staff.
OL,15,FWatch the robots in action here
OL,17,FAsda has been attempting to improve
OL,18,Fprofitability after several years of
OL,19,Flosing market share to rivals such as
OL,20,FAldi and Lidl under the ownership of
OL,21,Fprivate equity firm TDR Capital.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
