PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780611061
OL,3,CAsda set to axe 1,000 jobs as
OL,4,Csupermarket expands use of robots in
OL,5,Cwarehouses
OL,7,FExecutive chairman Allan Leighton was
OL,8,Fbrought in to revive Asda's fortunes
OL,9,Fin 2024.
OL,11,FLast week, Asda unveiled an expanded
OL,12,Ftechnology partnership with Ocado.
OL,14,FFrom 2027, Ocado's software will be
OL,15,Fused to manage much of Asda's online
OL,16,Fgrocery operation, including order
OL,17,Ffulfilment, stock management and home
OL,18,Fdelivery planning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780611061
OL,3,CAsda set to axe 1,000 jobs as
OL,4,Csupermarket expands use of robots in
OL,5,Cwarehouses
OL,7,FWhile the deal does not include
OL,8,FOcado's robotic warehouses, it
OL,9,Fhighlights the growing role of
OL,10,Ftechnology in retail operations.
OL,12,FAcross the sector, supermarkets are
OL,13,Finvesting heavily in automation and
OL,14,Fdigital systems as they seek to
OL,15,Fimprove efficiency and offset rising
OL,16,Flabour costs.
OL,18,FAsda has already been using the
OL,19,FRedline Robot automated system at its
OL,20,FMagna Park warehouse site in
OL,21,FLutterworth since 2013.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
