PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780611061
OL,3,CAsda set to axe 1,000 jobs as
OL,4,Csupermarket expands use of robots in
OL,5,Cwarehouses
OL,7,F"A thousand people losing their jobs
OL,8,Fto be replaced by robots sounds like
OL,9,Fsomething from a dystopian sci fi
OL,10,Fmovie but the warehouse industry is
OL,11,Fbecoming increasingly automated and
OL,12,Fit's impossible to stand in the way of
OL,13,Fprogress," Rachelle Wilkins, a
OL,14,FNational Officer for GMB, said.
OL,16,FShe added: "(Our) members are now very
OL,17,Fworried this is the thin end of the
OL,18,Fwage. What if Asda does the same thing
OL,19,Fwith its online food shopping network?
OL,20,FThousands of jobs could be lost."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@JO]xD@MpmxD@Qpn
