OL,3,CAsda set to axe 1,000 jobs as
OL,4,Csupermarket expands use of robots in
OL,5,Cwarehouses
OL,7,FAutomation in warehousing is not new.
OL,8,FSupermarkets, logistics firms and
OL,9,Fmanufacturers have been investing in
OL,10,Frobotics to increase productivity for
OL,11,Fmany years.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
