CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780611061
OL,3,CAsda set to axe 1,000 jobs as
OL,4,Csupermarket expands use of robots in
OL,5,Cwarehouses
OL,7,FThe UK Warehousing Association says
OL,8,Faround 760,000 people in the UK are
OL,9,Femployed in warehouses - a figure that
OL,10,Fsoared fifteen years ago as online
OL,11,Fshopping took over, but one that has
OL,12,Fremained broadly steady more recently.
OL,14,FRetail analysts say the incentive for
OL,15,Fretailers to invest in automation has
OL,16,Fbecome stronger, as they seek to
OL,17,Foffset rising employment costs,
OL,18,Fincluding increases in National
OL,19,FInsurance contributions and the
OL,20,FNational Living Wage introduced last
OL,21,FApril.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
