FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780611061
OL,3,CAsda set to axe 1,000 jobs as
OL,4,Csupermarket expands use of robots in
OL,5,Cwarehouses
OL,7,FA survey of 382 retailers,
OL,8,Fmanufacturers and logistics firms in
OL,9,Fthe UK by Savills, published in
OL,10,FFebruary, found that more than half of
OL,11,Fthem planned to invest in Artificial
OL,12,FIntelligence and warehouse robotics/
OL,13,Fautomation in the next three years.
OL,15,FOne in five said they thought they
OL,16,Fwould need fewer staff, but one in
OL,17,Fthree thought they would need more.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
