FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780611061
OL,3,CAsda set to axe 1,000 jobs as
OL,4,Csupermarket expands use of robots in
OL,5,Cwarehouses
OL,7,FIn a statement, an Asda spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "As we announced in January, we
OL,9,Fare partnering with DHL to ensure we
OL,10,Fcan continue to serve the growth in
OL,11,Four George online business effectively.
OL,13,F"Any colleague who currently works in
OL,14,Fthese roles will be transferred under
OL,15,FTUPE regulations to DHL. Asda will
OL,16,Fwork closely with DHL to support
OL,17,Fcolleagues through this process
OL,18,Fincluding considering alternative
OL,19,Femployment opportunities across both
OL,20,Fbusinesses."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
